{"tid":643065,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"97%交流北上　無國際實習名額","createTime":"2018-04-26T08:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T00:45:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"296a02e387fc11e08937f3642a82d6446b2b776a","tid":643065,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180426/20373213?_ga=2.83045142.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F20373213%3F_ga%3D2.83045142.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=oeDEK%2BPbL9vhbCeMb9fqlxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=9f760ce4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F20373213%3F_ga%3D2.83045142.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=101fb15c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180426/20373213?_ga=2.83045142.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月26日 <br />\n<br />\n97%交流北上　無國際實習名額<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180426/large/13414076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180426%2Flarge%2F13414076.jpg&h=dffee04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n審計署<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】審計報告質疑，民政事務局現時提供的青年交流及實習活動以內地項目為主，更無任何國際實習名額。署方促民政局在提供內地實習名額之外，考慮引進在其他國家實習的名額，亦有需要探討在更多國家舉辦青年交流活動，以進一步擴闊青年視野。事實上，近年政府大灑金錢搞內地交流團，過去3年民政局和教育局花5.3億元資助近25萬人到內地交流。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，2012/13至2015/16年度的726個青年交流及實習項目僅24個屬於中國以外的國家，佔3.3%，即中國佔96.7%。2016/17年度首推一帶一路交流資助計劃，令外國項目整體數量增至33個，佔9.2%，但仍然沒有國際實習名額。<br />\n<br />\n民政局表示同意審計署的建議，並稱政府致力擴闊在內地及海外國家交流及實習的機會，讓年輕人更了解當前國家和國際層面的經濟、社會和文化面貌，以及不同地方的工作文化和事業前景。<br />\n<br />\n政府文件顯示，在2015/16至2017/18的3年間，民政局每年資助逾2萬人到內地交流或實習，3年來共有6.5萬人受惠，涉及公帑3.1億元。教育局在此3年間，亦花2.2億元，資助18.2萬名專上、中、小學生到內地交流。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄧力行  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n有利益衝突　三委員照審批<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n75%名額無人去　軍訓營仍續辦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有利益衝突　三委員照審批<br />\n<br />\n75%名額無人去　軍訓營仍續辦<br />\n<br />\n昇達失299日排污紀錄　獲環保署放生<br />\n<br />\n路政署管理工程不善掘路延誤急增78%　最長封多16月<br />\n<br />\n民政懶理　葵涌公園空置17年<br />\n<br />\n八號幹線甩漏　路政署賠3.7億<br />\n<br />\n免費WiFi慢　38%不達標<br />\n<br />\n審計署轟民政局耗1.3億推青年內交　辦一人洗腦團"},{"pid":"830c09ef9f1a6567684bc97e072fecd18fdc5ed3","tid":643065,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T08:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041832a1ddd8351adb7fe35a2e35715603ddf439","tid":643065,"uid":37661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"返支那先有得貪<br />\n<br />\n去外國無呀<br />\n<br />\n點會搞丫。"},{"pid":"b074907389377393b227af05fa5795dd74d118b8","tid":643065,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fe884d67533b2b72ea608c5bee652e9cc71a00","tid":643065,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b966df4d3bddaf7af759381703579c62dcdc4597","tid":643065,"uid":182192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T09:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69aecb74c26a2b6542a7d4740603d3fad507867d","tid":643065,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T10:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96580ec471358a2e865db34cb583bb4f9fa03c6","tid":643065,"uid":170772,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T10:47:49.000Z","msg":"審計署係咪正式超越icac"},{"pid":"9763318e65be475a